# ============================================================
# Admin panel access switch.
# ============================================================
#
# By default the admin panel is OPEN (only protected by the
# PHP session-based login).
#
# To temporarily LOCK the entire admin panel — even before the
# login form loads — uncomment the 3 lines below (remove the
# leading "#" on each). Anyone hitting /admin/ will see a 403
# Forbidden until you re-comment them.
#
# Toggle via: cPanel → File Manager → Show Hidden Files →
#             admin/.htaccess → Edit.
#
# # <RequireAll>
# #   Require all denied
# # </RequireAll>
